    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel the moment you step inside. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and responsive as can be. It\u2019s practically in showroom condition, and I promise you won\u2019t find another one cared for quite like this. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel of something special!",
