    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously curated E92 M3, a true driver\u2019s specimen in showroom-grade condition. This S65 naturally aspirated V8 is a masterpiece of high-revving engineering, featuring a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline. I\u2019ve proactively addressed the critical failure points: VAC Motorsports coated rod bearings have been swapped in and throttle actuators replaced with uprated gears for indefinite reliability. The DCT transmission logic has been flashed for lightning-fast shift points, and the subframe has been thoroughly inspected with zero signs of stress. Suspension geometry is dialed in with Ohlins Road & Track coilovers, significantly reducing unsprung weight and sharpening turn-in response. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, preserved under a multi-stage ceramic coating. This is a precision instrument maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications. Zero oil consumption, no VANOS rattle, just pure mechanical symphony.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
